title: About
text: Yalemzewod Gelaw is a Postdoctoral Research Officer at the Telethon Kids Institute. His wider research interests are preventing and controlling infectious diseases including malaria, tuberculosis, and HIV in Low - and Middle-income Countries (LMICs) at low cost using Geostatistical models.
